#### ‚ÑπÔ∏è Hosts Info
<h4>
    
    Number of Blocked Domains: _hostsnum_
    Domain Blocklist size: _hostssize_
    
    Number of Blocked IPs: _ipnum_
    IP Blocklist size: _ipsize_
    
    Auto Updates: Every 24 hours
    
</h4>

